  m_text: "Hand Puzzles :\n\nChallenge your brain with five timeless games,\nreimagined
    for MR:\n\nSlide the Block \u2013 Shift tiles to free the main block\nTowers
    of Hanoi \u2013 Stack and solve this legendary logic puzzle\nStick Puzzles \u2013
    Rearrange matchsticks to correct the equation\nMarble Solitaire \u2013 Jump and
    eliminate marbles with strategy\nTangram Puzzle - Sharpen your mind and spatial
    \nskills\u2014combine colorful triangle pieces to recreate \nintricate shapes.\n\n\n"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
