  m_text: "Suggestions & Improvements\n\nWe\u2019re constantly refining the flick,
    the physics, and the 360-degree experience. If you have ideas on how to make
    the game even better\u2014or if you've spotted a bug in the arena\u2014we want
    to hear from you.\n\nDrop us a line at visionxr.opc@gmail.com. Your feedback
    helps us shape the future of this new tabletop evolution, and we\u2019ll be happy
    to roll out updates based on your input!"
